section.section.bg-gray
  .container
    header.section-header
      small Anticipated
      h2 Roadmap
      p.text-muted[style="font-size: 12px;"] The roadmap outlined below is subject to change based on user feedback, market conditions, and the competitive landscape; it is merely intended as an overview to explain the features that CoinFi intends to implement on the platform.
    #roadmap.accordion
      .card
        h5.card-title
          a.collapsed[data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#roadmap" href="#roadmap2018Q1"] 2018Q1: Platform Foundations
        #roadmap2018Q1.in.collapse
          .card-block
            ul
              li News and content aggregation overlaid on price charts per cryptocurrency
              li Obtain minute-level historical price data and market data feeds for cryptocurrencies
              li Develop editorial procedures, begin in-house compilation of news aggregation on existing cryptocurrencies
              li Search and filter functionality
              li User authentication and authorization
              li Social functionality including upvote/downvote and sharing
              li Prototype of machine learning algorithms for content classification, quality assurance, and fraud detection
              li Public beta of platform released
      .card
        h5.card-title
          a.collapsed[data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#roadmap" href="#roadmap2018Q2"] 2018Q2: Personalization
        #roadmap2018Q2.in.collapse
          .card-block
            ul
              li Custom cryptocurrency portfolio dashboard
              li Custom newsfeed / watchlist
              li Custom email subscriptions for specific cryptocurrency newsfeeds
              li Allow users to follow others’ portfolios
              li Initial beta versions of trading signals (see below)
      .card
        h5.card-title
          a.collapsed[data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#roadmap" href="#roadmap2018Q3"] 2018Q3: Premium Subscriptions
        #roadmap2018Q3.in.collapse
          .card-block
            ul
              li Accept staked tokens for advanced functionality and premium subscriptions
              li Sentiment analysis of real-time news data per cryptocurrency
              li Accept community content contributions
      .card
        h5.card-title
          a.collapsed[data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#roadmap" href="#roadmap2018Q4"] 2018Q4: Trading Signals
        #roadmap2018Q4.in.collapse
          .card-block
            ul
              li Abnormal volatility detection
              li Abnormal price movement detection
              li Abnormal volume detection
              li Increased social mention detection
              li Best price exchange identification
              li Best currency pair identification
              li Source code release detection
              li Launch premium subscription for trading signals
              li Accept community contributed trading signals
      .card
        h5.card-title
          a.collapsed[data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#roadmap" href="#roadmap2019Q1"] 2019Q1: Trading Algorithms
        #roadmap2019Q1.in.collapse
          .card-block
            ul
              li VWAP (Volume Weighted Average Price)
              li TWAP (Time Weighted Average Price)
              li BWAP (Block Weighted Average Price)
              li Sniper
              li % of Volume
              li Target Close
              li Implementation Shortfall
              li Launch premium subscription for trading algorithms
              li Accept community contributed trading algorithms
      .card
        h5.card-title
          a.collapsed[data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#roadmap" href="#roadmap2019Q2"] 2019Q2: Auction Framework
        #roadmap2019Q2.in.collapse
          .card-block
            ul
              li Develop auction platform
              li Private auctions
              li Dutch auction
              li Reverse auction
              li Build ability to leave reviews on vendor quality
              li Escrow service for auction payment
      .card
        h5.card-title
          a.collapsed[data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#roadmap" href="#roadmap2019Q3"] 2019Q3: Combining and Customizing Signals
        #roadmap2019Q3.in.collapse
          .card-block
            ul
              li Platform architecture for custom signals
              li UI/UX for developing custom signals
              li Drag and drop functionality to combine signals
              li Custom alerting
